!! conditional-exports

Example, different files are loaded if package is `import`ed or `require`d:
Same rules as in [[Import example]]

```json
// ./node_modules/pkg/package.json
{
  "type": "module",
  "main": "./index.cjs",
  "exports": {
    "import": "./index.mjs",
    "require": "./index.cjs"
  }
}
```

